'''積遜·高馬斯'''（{{lang-en|Jason Koumas}}，{{bd|1979年|9月25日|catIdx=Koumas, Jason}}）出生於[[雷克瑟姆|雷克瑟姆]]，是一名[[威爾斯|威爾斯]][[足球員|足球員]]，司職[[中場|中場]]，是前[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯國腳]]。

高馬斯（[[希腊语|希腊语]]：Ιασωνας Κούμας）是[[希臘人|希裔]][[賽普勒斯|賽普勒斯]]人。

==生平==
===球會===
;早年
高馬斯出身於[[利物浦足球俱乐部|利物浦]]青訓學院，同期隊友還有[[史提芬·謝拉特|謝拉特]]及[[迈克尔·欧文|奧雲]]等。但他其後沒有與利物浦簽署學徒合約，轉投低級別的[[特兰米尔流浪者足球俱乐部|燦美爾]]。
 
;燦美爾
高馬斯於1998/99年球季開始在燦美爾展開[[職業|職業]]球員事業，在效力4年間連串出色的表現，使他贏得無數的讚譽，包括獲選入2001/02年[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英乙〈第三級〉]]「[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA年度最佳陣容]]」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2002-04-15 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/1930633.stm |title=Double joy for Zamora |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2003-04-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030423172037/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_div_2/1930633.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，高馬斯為視為前途無限的年青天才球員。2000/01年[[英格蘭足總盃|英格蘭足總盃]]燦美爾爆冷在[[葛迪遜公園球場|葛迪遜公園球場]]以3-0擯走[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]，高馬斯是入球球員之一<small><ref>{{cite web |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/1138678.stm |title=Tranmere shame Everton |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=27 January 2001 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2003-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20030811140001/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/fa_cup/1138678.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。他的潛質終於在2002年8月被時任[[西布罗姆维奇足球俱乐部|西布朗]]領隊[[加利·麥臣|加利·麥臣]]（Gary Megson）發掘到，付出225萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]將他收歸旗下<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2002-08-29 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/2208534.stm |title=West Brom tie up Koumas deal |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10}}</ref></small>。

;西布朗
跳升兩級的高馬斯在[[英超|英超]]首季表現出色，在對[[曼徹斯特聯足球俱樂部|曼聯]]及[[布莱克本流浪者足球俱乐部|布力般流浪]]個人獨力射入精彩入球，贏得球隊「年度最佳球員」獎項<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2003-04-29 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/2985693.stm |title=Koumas wins West Brom award |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10}}</ref></small>，但他的表現不足以挽救西布朗免於降班。

翌年高馬斯即帶領球隊獲得[[英格蘭足球聯賽|英甲〈第二級〉聯賽]]亞軍重返[[英超|英超]]，期間於2003年11月獲選「每月最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2003-12-03 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/3288439.stm |title=Koumas named player of the month |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2003-12-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031205181538/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/3288439.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，同時亦入選英甲〈第二級〉「[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA年度最佳陣容]]」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2004-04-25 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/3628905.stm |title=Henry retains PFA crown |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-07-25 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6jH3avQWg?url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/3628905.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。一度提出轉會要求的高馬斯於2004年夏季與西布朗續約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2004-07-15 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/3881955.stm |title=Koumas commits to Baggies |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2004-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040718021319/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/3881955.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但在新球季他繼續與領隊加利·麥臣鬧不和，更被眨與青年軍一同訓練，加利·麥臣掛冠後，新任領隊[[布莱恩·罗布森|白賴仁·笠臣]]再次起用高馬斯<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/4063497.stm |title=Robson gives Koumas second chance |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2004-12-02 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022130105/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/4063497.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，惟最終笠臣表示對高馬斯的態度感到失望，並將他掛牌求售<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2005-05-13 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/4543763.stm |title=West Brom put Koumas up for sale |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10}}</ref></small>。

[[2005年至2006年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|2005/06年球季]]季初高馬斯被外借[[英冠|英冠]]的[[威爾斯|威爾斯]]球會[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]，為期12個月<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2005-07-27 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/4648787.stm |title=Koumas seals Cardiff loan switch |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2007-09-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070914052637/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/4648787.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，這次借用隨即獲得成功，於聯賽揭幕戰主場迎戰[[列斯聯足球會|列斯聯]]，下半場入替的高馬斯射入扳平1-1，首次上陣即取得入球，最終協助球隊2-1獲勝打嚮頭砲<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4126998.stm |title=Cardiff 2-1 Leeds |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-08-09 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307071704/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_div_1/4126998.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在餘下的球季，高馬斯持續表現出色，往往能憑一己之力為球隊贏取-{比}-賽，於上陣44場射入13球，深受「藍鳥」球迷的擁戴，除獲選球會「年度最佳球員」外，再獲選入[[英冠|英冠]]「[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA年度最佳陣容]]」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2006-04-24 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_of_wales/4939930.stm |title=Welsh stars in team of the year |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2006-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060427160619/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/league_of_wales/4939930.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。季中笠臣表示如價錢合適，卡迪夫城可以買斷高馬斯<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/4534254.stm |title=West Brom prepared to sell Koumas |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2005-12-16 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310101401/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/4534254.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，其後提議卡迪夫城可以[[卡梅隆·杰罗梅|謝路美]]交換高馬斯<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5000694.stm |title=Robson warns Cardiff over Koumas |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-05-20 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-10-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161030200305/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5000694.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而西布朗亦於來季降班到[[英冠|英冠]]。

高馬斯在夏季小休後沒有返回西布朗報到而面臨球會的紀律處分<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5179678.stm |title=Koumas disciplined by West Brom |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-14 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020044518/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5179678.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，卡迪夫城於[[2006年至2007年英格蘭足球冠軍聯賽|新球季]]展開前正式向西布朗出價收購高馬斯，但其100萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]，附加如獲升班再加100萬英鎊的出價被西布朗一口拒絕<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5117122.stm |title=West Brom reject bid for Koumas |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-17 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160310101438/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5117122.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，西布朗要求即付150萬英鎊，另附加條款50萬英鎊，更拒絕借用要求<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5191198.stm |title=Cardiff criticise Baggies' stance |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-07-18 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307122015/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5191198.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，最終卡迪夫城以資金不足而結束收購商討<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5259880.stm |title=Cardiff end Koumas transfer saga |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-08-18 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307064626/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/5259880.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在兩會商討期間，高馬斯實行罷踢及拒絕返回山楂球場（Hawthorns），更獨自操練以保持狀態。2006年8月23日再食回頭草，與西布朗簽署三年新約，再次投入球隊的訓練<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5279716.stm |title=Koumas signs new Baggies contract |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-08-23 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2019-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190328121903/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5279716.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。而在笠臣於季初因戰績不振而提前解約<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5355924.stm |title=Robson and West Brom part company |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-09-18 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2018-05-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180521013600/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/5355924.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，由[[托尼·莫布雷|托尼·莫布雷]]（Tony Mowbray）接手執教後，高馬斯在西布朗取得重生，成為球隊正選主力，在多場-{比}-賽表現出色，獲選[[英冠|英冠]]「12月份最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Koumas handed Championship award |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/6270507.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-01-17 |accessdate=2010-03-10}}</ref></small>，更於2007年3月4日「英格蘭聯賽頒獎禮」獲頒「英冠年度最佳球員」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |title=Koumas handed Championship award |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/6418171.stm |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2007-03-04 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2007-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070324092939/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/6418171.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，及連續兩年入選[[英冠|英冠]]「[[PFA年度最佳陣容|PFA年度最佳陣容]]」<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-04-22 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6582201.stm |title=Ronaldo secures PFA awards double |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2008-04-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080414212009/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/6582201.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

;韋根
2007年7月西布朗接納[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|韋根]]要求收購高馬斯的530萬[[英鎊|英鎊]]出價，表示是一個理想的價格，高馬斯於7月10日通過體檢正式加盟，簽約四年，並表示欣賞時任領隊[[基斯·赫澄斯|基斯·赫澄斯]]（Chris Hutchings）的理念才轉投韋根<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/6748685.stm |title=Wigan complete signing of Koumas |accessdate=2010-310 |date=2007-07-10 |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |archive-date=2007-10-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071009000436/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/6748685.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，他於8月11日首次披甲，1-2作客負於[[埃弗顿足球俱乐部|愛華頓]]<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-08-11 |url=http://www.wiganlatics.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0,,10429~37419,00.html |title=Everton vs Wigan Athletic |publisher=[[威根竞技足球俱乐部|''wiganlatics.premiumtv.co.uk'']] |accessdate=2010-03-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071217182619/http://www.wiganlatics.premiumtv.co.uk/page/MatchReport/0%2C%2C10429~37419%2C00.html |archivedate=2007-12-17 }}</ref></small>；翌月高馬斯以入球慶祝其第300場聯賽上陣，主場1-1賽和[[富勒姆足球俱乐部|富咸]]於80分鐘射入[[十二碼|十二碼]]扳平，亦是加盟以來首個入球<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |date=2007-09-15 |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6984886.stm |title=Wigan 1-1 Fulham |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2013-12-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131227032204/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport1/hi/football/eng_prem/6984886.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。由於受傷患困擾，加上[[斯蒂夫·布鲁斯|布魯士]]上任後喜用踢法硬朗的中場，高馬斯效力韋根3年來上陣機會不多<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_4454657,00.html |title=Koumas targets starting role |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2008-11-04 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160309155658/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11661_4454657,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。 

[[2009年至2010年英格蘭超級聯賽|2009/10年球季]][[罗伯托·马丁内斯|馬天尼斯]]接手任教韋根一度重燃高馬斯的競賽希望<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8200706.stm |title=Martinez hails 'magician' Koumas |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-13 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020042829/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8200706.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，聯賽揭幕戰作客對[[阿士東維拉足球會|阿士東維拉]]，正選上陣的高馬斯射入一球為球隊鎖定2-0勝局<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8197493.stm |title=Aston Villa 0-2 Wigan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-08-15 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200418042547/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/eng_prem/8197493.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。在開季首6場取得5次正選上陣後，高馬斯再被打入冷宮，上半季僅再獲3次上陣機會。2010年2月馬天尼斯表示有兩支球隊有意借用高馬斯，希望外借能使他回復狀態<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/8518343.stm |title=Wigan happy for Jason Koumas to leave on loan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-16 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307191719/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/wigan_athletic/8518343.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，舊球會西布朗相信是其中之一<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/west-bromwich-albion-fc/west-bromwich-albion-fc-news/2010/02/10/west-brom-may-swoop-for-jason-joumas-on-loan-97319-25806636/ |title=West Brom may swoop for Jason Koumas on loan |publisher=''birminghammail.net'' |date=2010-02-10 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2010-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100421164015/http://www.birminghammail.net/birmingham-sport/west-bromwich-albion-fc/west-bromwich-albion-fc-news/2010/02/10/west-brom-may-swoop-for-jason-joumas-on-loan-97319-25806636/ |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，但其後領隊[[罗伯托·迪马特奥|迪馬堤奧]]表示借用計畫沒有進展<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/8516414.stm |title=West Bromwich Albion's Jara set to miss rest of season |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-02-15 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307135835/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/w/west_bromwich_albion/8516414.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，而[[纽卡斯尔联足球俱乐部|紐卡素]]亦否認借用<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5970793,00.html |title=Magpies rule out Koumas deal |publisher=Sky Sports |date=2010-02-22 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2010-02-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100226122222/http://www.skysports.com/story/0,19528,11095_5970793,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2010年8月7日高馬斯獲得再次外借到[[英冠|英冠]]球會[[卡迪夫城足球俱乐部|卡迪夫城]]一個球季<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8886787.stm |title=Cardiff City complete Jason Koumas loan move |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2010-08-07 |accessdate=2010-08-09 |archive-date=2020-10-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201024162448/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/c/cardiff_city/8886787.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

===國家隊===
高馬斯是一名希裔塞浦路斯[[炸鱼薯条|炸鱼]]店東主的兒子，有資格代表[[塞浦路斯國家足球隊|塞浦路斯]]或[[威爾斯足球代表隊|威爾斯]]，當時任威爾斯領隊的[[馬克·曉士|馬克·曉士]]向他招手時<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/wales/1218983.stm |title=Koumas accepts Wales invitation |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-03-15 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022180110/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/wales/1218983.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，高馬斯最終選擇代表出生地參加國際賽<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tranmere_rovers/1247799.stm |title=Koumas set to opt for Wales |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2001-03-28 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022192341/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/teams/t/tranmere_rovers/1247799.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2001年首次代表國家隊上陣對[[烏克蘭國家足球隊|烏克蘭]]。他亦是威爾斯角逐[[2004年歐洲足球錦標賽|2004年歐國盃]]外圍賽參賽球員之一，最終於附加賽0-1僅負[[俄羅斯國家足球隊|俄羅斯]]而失去晉級決賽週的資格。

2008年6月1日威爾斯作客[[荷蘭國家足球隊|荷蘭]]為對手參賽[[2008年欧洲足球锦标赛|2008年歐國盃]]進行熱身，高馬斯首次戴上國家隊[[隊長_(足球)|隊長]]臂章參賽，以0-2落敗而回<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7426243.stm |title=Netherlands 2-0 Wales |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2006-06-01 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810230610/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7426243.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。2008年9月6日威爾斯的[[2010年世界盃外圍賽_(歐洲區)|2010年世界盃外圍賽]]首場分組賽對[[阿塞拜疆國家足球隊|阿塞拜疆]]，高馬斯射失一球[[十二碼|十二碼]]，幸而[[森·禾基斯|森·禾基斯]]末段時間的入球，挽救威爾斯免於主場失分於[[弱旅|弱旅]]腳下<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7590218.stm |title=Wales 1-0 Azerbaijan |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2008-09-06 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2009-09-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090905055917/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7590218.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

2009年9月6日高馬斯宣佈從國家隊退役<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8240621.stm |title=Koumas announces Wales retirement |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-09-06 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2020-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022221425/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/8240621.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>，合共上陣34場及射入10球，3月28日0-2主場負於[[芬蘭國家足球隊|芬蘭]]是他最後一次為國家隊上陣<small><ref>{{cite news |language=en |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7921623.stm |title=Wales 0-2 Finland |publisher=[[BBC|BBC]] Sport |date=2009-03-28 |accessdate=2010-03-10 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307163720/http://news.bbc.co.uk/sport2/hi/football/internationals/7921623.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref></small>。

